# Support

## Questions

For usage questions or general guidance, open a GitHub issue and describe the
package or repository area involved.

## Bugs

Use the bug issue template for problems with:

- package behavior or published guidance
- repository documentation or structure
- GitHub-facing governance or collaboration files

## Feature Requests

Use the feature issue template for:

- package improvements
- repository documentation or structure improvements
- governance or contributor guidance improvements

## Security Issues

Do not report security-sensitive issues through normal bug reports. Follow
`SECURITY.md` instead.
